Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.96,0:00:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起丈夫更爱公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.00,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.00,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.00,0:00:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.94,0:00:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.61,0:00:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.88,0:00:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.55,0:00:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.75,0:00:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后要受您照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.15,0:00:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.62,0:01:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带了很多行李吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.02,0:01:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.89,0:01:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.45,0:01:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶  这些要搬到什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.65,0:01:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟   不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.59,0:01:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等   我换件衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.99,0:01:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.78,0:02:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹   能来这里帮个忙么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.99,0:02:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.65,0:02:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.79,0:02:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把门打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.80,0:02:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些放这边可以么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.07,0:02:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦您了\N好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.34,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳烦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.08,0:04:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样对你来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好机会   不过以后要辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公以前也是在飞机上做的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做过一小段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.77,0:04:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到今天为止不在家的时候很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.38,0:04:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后可能让她留下更多寂寞的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.45,0:04:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为母亲不在  老爹你也很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.59,0:04:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.79,0:05:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家里人可以同心协力  互相帮助吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.93,0:05:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子会说漂亮话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.47,0:05:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子会说漂亮话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你安心出门工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.45,0:05:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片很让人怀念呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是晶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜空姐考试合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是教官您的功劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会特地的过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.03,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服来了   无论如何都想让您看一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常适合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我儿子光一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个见习飞行员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后你们可能会一起工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可以和您一起拍张照么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸?和我拍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那我来拍  老爹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.67,0:07:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹  机会难得  穿上制服怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.21,0:07:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿制服更好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.28,0:07:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿照相机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.15,0:07:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  真没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹我要拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹  我要拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帽子戴上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帽子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了么  看这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.04,0:08:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 再来一张  再来一张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微再靠近一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.33,0:08:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么辛苦才合格的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.53,0:08:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚后马上就辞职了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公你为什么做教官不做飞行员了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.88,0:08:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在她身边多陪陪她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然光一让你留下了寂寞的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.76,0:08:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还请支持他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.77,0:22:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.00,0:22:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公  不吃么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.07,0:22:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微想起一点事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.81,0:23:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.54,0:25:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联络不上有点担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.42,0:25:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就能回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.16,0:25:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道几点路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.16,0:25:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了  路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.77,0:25:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天光一好像能回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.98,0:25:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不高兴么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.92,0:26:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光一  是个很好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.39,0:26:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得自己配不上他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.60,0:26:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  还是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.67,0:26:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有喜欢的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.74,0:26:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了忘记那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.47,0:26:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.81,0:26:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  还是忘不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.44,0:26:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.38,0:27:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.19,0:27:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.99,0:27:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.53,0:27:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:44.76,0:27:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.16,0:27:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.76,0:27:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.10,0:27:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公\N我要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.50,0:27:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.17,0:27:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.97,0:27:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.60,0:28:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样有感觉么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.13,0:28:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.13,0:28:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶   还不住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.35,0:28:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道自己在做什么么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.76,0:28:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:25.79,0:29:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:28.20,0:29:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要舔  舔公公的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:32.07,0:29:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很想舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.07,0:29:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来脱  要看肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.15,0:29:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶  不能这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:40.67,0:30:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公  公公  全部让我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.88,0:30:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经硬了啊  公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.57,0:31:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然硬了  不是么  公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.05,0:31:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太雄伟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.92,0:31:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.06,0:31:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.59,0:31:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:55.01,0:31:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.00,0:32:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:00.14,0:33:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底明白自己在做什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:05.48,0:33:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.48,0:33:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.16,0:33:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.16,0:33:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.94,0:34:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真舒服  公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.21,0:34:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.36,0:34:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多揉揉我的屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.04,0:34:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对   就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:57.19,0:35:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多揉揉  您真懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:30.69,0:35:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妤舒服   好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.56,0:35:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公  您真擅长  公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.72,0:36:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.46,0:36:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真擅长 对  就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:17.67,0:36:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:35.02,0:36:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.05,0:37:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶  晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:00.92,0:37:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.48,0:37:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经停不下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.82,0:37:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多舔舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.16,0:37:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.20,0:38:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 不行了  要高朝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.20,0:38:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要高潮了  高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.36,0:38:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.78,0:40:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:56.41,0:41:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:45.93,0:42:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:48.86,0:42:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.75,0:43:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.61,0:44:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:06.27,0:44:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.83,0:46:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  高潮了  高潮了  高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:40.89,0:47:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了   你太诱人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:46.09,0:47:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公公的肉棒真热  真热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:53.63,0:48:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:43.28,0:49:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高潮了  高潮了  高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:04.77,0:50:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:08.24,0:50:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好厉害
